            </p>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/customerRegister" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium shadow-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-200">
                Get Started Today
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Product Overview Section -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">Why Choose MediVerse?</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-blue-500 text-4xl mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Streamlined Operations</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Automate inventory management, prescription processing, and customer records in one intuitive platform, saving valuable time and reducing errors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-green-500 text-4xl mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Data-Driven Insights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Make informed decisions with real-time analytics on sales trends, inventory levels, and customer preferences to optimize your pharmacy business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-purple-500 text-4xl mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Enhanced Customer Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Provide a seamless experience with digital prescriptions, refill reminders, and personalized health recommendations for your customers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Dashboard Section -->
  <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">Dashboard Overview</h2>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12 justify-center">
      <% const stats = [
      { title: 'Admins', count: admins, bgColor: 'bg-blue-500', textColor: 'text-blue-100', icon: 'fa-user-shield' }, 
      { title: 'Customers', count: customers, bgColor: 'bg-green-500', textColor: 'text-green-100', icon: 'fa-users' },
      { title: 'Feedbacks', count: feedbacks, bgColor: 'bg-purple-500', textColor: 'text-purple-100', icon: 'fa-comment-dots' }, 
      { title: 'Medicines', count: medicines, bgColor: 'bg-yellow-500', textColor: 'text-yellow-100', icon: 'fa-pills' }, 
      { title: 'Suppliers', count: suppliers, bgColor: 'bg-red-500', textColor: 'text-red-100', icon: 'fa-truck' },
      { title: 'Purchases', count: purchases, bgColor: 'bg-orange-500', textColor: 'text-orange-100', icon: 'fa-shopping-cart' }, 
      { title: 'Payments', count: payments, bgColor: 'bg-blue-500', textColor: 'text-blue-100', icon: 'fa-credit-card' }, 
      { title: 'Invoice', count: invoice, bgColor: 'bg-purple-500', textColor: 'text-purple-100', icon: 'fa-file-invoice-dollar' }, 
      { title: 'Stocks', count: stocks, bgColor: 'bg-gray-500', textColor: 'text-gray-100', icon: 'fa-boxes' }
    ];%>


      <% stats.forEach(stat => { %>
      <div class="transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="relative <%= stat.bgColor %> rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-3 -mr-3 <%= stat.bgColor.replace('-500', '-400') %> rounded-full p-2">
            <i class="fas <%= stat.icon %> text-white text-xl"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">
              <%= stat.title %>
            </h3>
            <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline justify-between">
              <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">
                <%= stat.count %>
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium <%= stat.textColor %>">Active</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">Key Features</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-100 p-3 rounded-full">
              <i class="fas fa-pills text-yellow-500 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-semibold">Comprehensive Medicine Management</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Track every aspect of your pharmacy inventory from purchase to expiry. Set automatic alerts for low stock and expiring medicines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-green-100 p-3 rounded-full">
              <i class="fas fa-truck text-green-500 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-semibold">Supplier Relationship Management</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Maintain detailed supplier profiles, track order history, and manage pricing negotiations all in one place.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 p-3 rounded-full">
              <i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar text-blue-500 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-semibold">Advanced Billing & Invoicing</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Generate professional invoices, track payments, and manage insurance claims with our intuitive financial tools.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 p-3 rounded-full">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-pie text-purple-500 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-semibold">Business Analytics</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Gain insights into sales trends, popular medicines, and customer behavior with comprehensive analytical reports.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Customer Feedback Section -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">What Our Customers Say</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <% getfeedbacks.forEach(fb=> { %>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full p-1">
                <img src="<%= fb.customer_photo %>" alt="<%= fb.customer_name %>" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full">
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                  <%= fb.customer_name %>
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Verified Customer</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"<%= fb.feedback_text %>"</p>
            <div class="mt-2 text-yellow-500">
              <% for (let i = 0; i < fb.rating; i++) { %> ‚≠ê <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Top Selling Medicines Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">Top Selling Medicines</h2>
      <% if (topSelling.length > 0) { %>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <% topSelling.forEach(med => { %>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 overflow-hidden p-6">
          <% if (med.photo) { %>
          <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,<%= med.photo.toString('base64') %>" alt="<%= med.name %>" class="w-fit h-fit object-cover rounded-md mb-3">
          <% } else { %>
          <img src="/img/noImg.jpg" alt="No Image Available" class="w-fit h-fit object-cover rounded-md mb-3">
          <% } %>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800"><%= med.name || "Unknown Medicine" %></h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Category: <%= med.category || "N/A" %></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Sold: <%= med.sold_count || 0 %> units</p>
          <p class="text-gray-800 font-bold mt-2">$<%= med.price || "N/A" %></p>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
      <% } else { %>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">No top-selling medicines available.</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <!-- Customer Growth Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">üìà Customer Growth</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <p class="text-gray-600">New Customers This Month: <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold"><%= newCustomers %></span></p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Total Registered Customers: <span class="text-green-600 font-bold"><%= customers %></span></p>
        <canvas id="customerGrowthChart"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      var ctx = document.getElementById('customerGrowthChart').getContext('2d');
      var customerGrowthChart = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: 'line',
        data: {
          labels: <%- JSON.stringify(days.map(day => day.substring(5))) %>,
          datasets: [{
            label: 'New Customers',
            data: <%- JSON.stringify(customerData) %>,
            borderColor: '#3B82F6',
            backgroundColor: 'rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2)',
            borderWidth: 2,
            fill: true
          }]
        }
      });
    </script>

    <!-- Pricing Plans Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">Upgrade Your Pharmacy Plan</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Standard Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-blue-400">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-4">Standard</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">&#8377; 1999<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">/month</span></p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Basic Inventory Management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Prescription Upload & Tracking</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Automated Billing & Invoicing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">2 Admin Users</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="/customerRegister" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-200">Upgrade Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Premium Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-green-400 transform scale-105">
          <div class="bg-green-500 py-2">
            <p class="text-center text-white font-semibold">Best Value</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-4">Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">&#8377; 4999<span class="text-sm text-gray-600">/month</span></p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Advanced Inventory & Expiry Tracking</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">24/7 Prescription Management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-600">Loyalty & Discount Management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
